{"book": 24, "chapter": 17, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "猶大的罪和懲罰"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 猶大的罪是用鐵筆、用金鋼鑽記錄的，銘刻在他們的心版上和壇角上。 "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們的兒女記念他們高岡上、青翠樹旁的壇和木偶。 "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我田野的山哪，我必因你在四境之內所犯的罪，把你的貨物、財寶，並邱壇當掠物交給仇敵； "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "並且你因自己的罪必失去我所賜給你的產業。我也必使你在你所不認識的地上服事你的仇敵；因為你使我怒中起火，直燒到永遠。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "訓誨集"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "倚靠人血肉的膀臂，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "心中離棄耶和華的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那人有禍了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因他必像沙漠的杜松，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不見福樂來到，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "卻要住曠野乾旱之處，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "無人居住的鹼地。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "倚靠耶和華、以耶和華為可靠的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那人有福了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他必像樹栽於水旁，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在河邊扎根，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "炎熱來到，並不懼怕，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "葉子仍必青翠，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在乾旱之年毫無掛慮，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "而且結果不止。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "人心比萬物都詭詐，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "壞到極處，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "誰能識透呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我－耶和華是鑒察人心、試驗人肺腑的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要照各人所行的和他做事的結果報應他。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那不按正道得財的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "好像鷓鴣菢不是自己下的蛋；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "到了中年，那財都必離開他，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他終久成為愚頑人。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我們的聖所是榮耀的寶座，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從太初安置在高處。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華－以色列的盼望啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "凡離棄你的必致蒙羞。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 耶和華說：離開我的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的名字必寫在土裏，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為他們離棄我這活水的泉源。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶利米求耶和華幫助"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華啊，求你醫治我，我便痊癒，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "拯救我，我便得救；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因你是我所讚美的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們對我說：耶和華的話在哪裏呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "叫這話應驗吧！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "至於我，那跟從你作牧人的職分，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我並沒有急忙離棄，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也沒有想那災殃的日子；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是你知道的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我口中所出的言語都在你面前。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "不要使我因你驚恐；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "當災禍的日子，你是我的避難所。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "願那些逼迫我的蒙羞，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "卻不要使我蒙羞；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們驚惶，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "卻不要使我驚惶；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使災禍的日子臨到他們，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "以加倍的毀壞毀壞他們。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "關於遵守安息日"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華對我如此說：「你去站在平民的門口，就是猶大君王出入的門，又站在耶路撒冷的各門口， "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "對他們說：『你們這猶大君王和猶大眾人，並耶路撒冷的一切居民，凡從這些門進入的都當聽耶和華的話。 "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說：你們要謹慎，不要在安息日擔甚麼擔子進入耶路撒冷的各門； "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "也不要在安息日從家中擔出擔子去。無論何工都不可做，只要以安息日為聖日，正如我所吩咐你們列祖的。』 "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們卻不聽從，不側耳而聽，竟硬着頸項不聽，不受教訓。」"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：「你們若留意聽從我，在安息日不擔甚麼擔子進入這城的各門，只以安息日為聖日，在那日無論何工都不做； "}, {"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那時就有坐大衛寶座的君王和首領，他們與猶大人，並耶路撒冷的居民，或坐車，或騎馬，進入這城的各門，而且這城必存到永遠。 "}, {"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "也必有人從猶大城邑和耶路撒冷四圍的各處，從便雅憫地、高原、山地，並南地而來，都帶燔祭、平安祭、素祭，和乳香，並感謝祭，到耶和華的殿去。 "}, {"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們若不聽從我，不以安息日為聖日，仍在安息日擔擔子，進入耶路撒冷的各門，我必在各門中點火；這火也必燒毀耶路撒冷的宮殿，不能熄滅。」"}]}]}